<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM8.4">
<l>tāmaraimē layaṉavaṉaip paṭaittavaṉē tayarataṉṟaṉ</l>
<l>māmatalāy maitilitaṉ maṇavāḷā vaṇṭiṉaṅkaḷ</l>
<l>kāmaraṅka ḷicaipāṭum kaṇapuratteṉ karumaṇiyē</l>
<l>yēmaruvuñ cilaivalavā yirākavaṉē tālēlō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You who created that Brahmā on the lotus!</l>
<l>O Daśaratha’s great Son! O Maithilī’s Husband!</l>
<l>O Apple of my eye from Kaṇapuram, where swarms of bees hum the kāmaram music!</l>
<l>O You who are capable [of mastering] the bow combined with arrows! O Rāghava! Tālēlō!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
